---
description: Auto-sync project changes to GitHub after each task
alwaysApply: true
---

After completing any task that changes project files:

1. Stage all relevant changes (`git add`).
2. Commit with a clear message describing what was done.
3. Push to `origin` on the current branch (`git push`).

Remote: https://github.com/kmd379-wq/Vird

If push fails due to auth, tell the user to sign in to GitHub in Cursor (Source Control panel) and retry.
